https://www.getpostman.com/downloads/
Bajar en linux 64

sudo yum install libXScrnSaver-1.2.2-6.1.el7.x86_64

Ejecutar ./Postman

Crear un request en postman
Seleccionar Oauth 2.0

En Get New Access Token completar los siguientes datos:

Fill in the settings configuration with the following information: 
Callback URL: https://openidconnect.net/callback 
Auth URL: http://sso.apps.lab.example.com/auth/realms/jb240/protocol/openid-connect/auth
Access Token URL: http://sso.apps.lab.example.com/auth/realms/jb240/protocol/openid-connect/token 
Client ID: 059e3882 (TU CLIENT ID)
Client Secret: addb491b9073b288052f0f105b6bcaea (TU CLIENT SECRET)

Generar un token


Para entrar a keycloack
